497/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=N+Engl+J+Med&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;pages=909&amp;doi=10.1056%2FNEJM199609263351301&amp;pmid=8782497">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">23.</div><div id="R23" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-firstauthor"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-snm">Boraschi</span><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-fnm">P</span></span>, Donati F. Complications of orthotopic liver transplantation: imaging findings. <em>Abdom Imaging</em>2004; 29: 189–202.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00261-003-0109-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15290945/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Abdom+Imaging&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;pages=189&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00261-003-0109-8&amp;pmid=15290945">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">24.</div><div id="R24" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-firstauthor"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-snm">Bridges</span><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-fnm">MD</span></span>, May GR, Harnois DM. Diagnosing biliary complications of orthotopic liver transplantation with mangafodipir trisodium-enhanced MR cholangiography: comparison with conventional MR cholangiography. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em>2004; 182: 1497–1504.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.182.6.1821497">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.n